@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bkadre(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 + 0.27)
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v1 + 0.79) + (v2 + 0.63 + v0 + 0.89)))
    tmp = v2
    v1 = (wp.cos(v2) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.33) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.19)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.00 + v1 + 0.82)))
    tmp = v0
    v0 = (tmp + wp.sin((v0 + 0.14 + v0 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
